sql:
SELECT AVG(rating) AS average_rating
FROM restaurant_ratings
WHERE restaurant_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- "Locations" refers to the city and country where each restaurant is located; 
- "City and country statistics" include the number of restaurants and the average rating in each city and country; 
- "Top cities" are those that do not have a parent city, serving as the roots of the hierarchy.
